room_title: Escape room "Laboratory "X"" by Let Me Out Escape Rooms in Houston
room_address: 16677 W Airport Blvd Sugar Land, TX 77498
room_description: Once a year the government opens their testing facility to the public as part of a public relations event. A friend encourages you to attend the event and tour with them this year. During your tour you notice a door labeled “Restricted Area” which piques your curiosity. Your tour guide quickly skips past the room on the tour which heightens your curiosity even more. You convince your friend to separate from the tour group and find out what is really behind that forbidden door. What you find is not only a threat to national security but also a threat to mankind. Do you have the guts to get out of the facility in time to expose them?
